Package: bartXViz
Title: Visualization of BART and BARP using SHAP
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The contribution of variables in Bayesian Additive Regression Trees (BART) 
  and Bayesian Additive Regression Trees with Post-Stratification (BARP) models 
  is computed using permutation-based Shapley values. The computed SHAP values 
  are then utilized to visualize the contribution of each variable through various plots.
